data.description: Why wait for new construction! Eligible for the $10K Welcome Home Grant. This stunning 3 level townhome awaits a new buyer. This dwelling is in move in ready condition with tons of upgraded finishes.  Finished basement with recess lights and walkout access to a fenced in backyard. The lower level has garage access, additional storage space and a powder room. Heading up to the main level, you  are greeted with beautiful natural oak hardwood floors throughout. The kitchen is spacious with ample cabinet and countertop space plus a pantry. Deck access and eat in kitchen/dining area. Secondary powder room on the main level. An open airy living room with tons of windows for natural light to illuminate the room. Washer and dryer is located on the bedroom level. 3 spacious bedrooms. The owner's suite has overhead lighting, ample closet and bedroom space. The owner's bath has a separate tub and frameless shower and dual vanities. Home warranty policy active and transferable to new buyer.
